### Test API Endpoints

### Get all authors
GET https://localhost:7000/api/authors
Accept: application/json

### Get author by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/authors/1
Accept: application/json

### Create new author
POST https://localhost:7000/api/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gabriel García Márquez",
  "birthDate": "1927-03-06",
  "nationality": "Colombiana"
}

### Update author
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/authors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Gabriel García Márquez",
  "birthDate": "1927-03-06",
  "nationality": "Colombiana"
}

### Delete author
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/authors/1

### Get all books
GET https://localhost:7000/api/books
Accept: application/json

### Get book by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/books/1
Accept: application/json

### Search books
GET https://localhost:7000/api/books/search?title=cien&genre=Ficción&authorName=García
Accept: application/json

### Create new book
POST https://localhost:7000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

